snippet: Cappie Pondexter and the new acquisition Tina Charles helped the Liberty roll in Connecticut against the No. 1 draft pick Chiney Ogwumike in the opener for both teams.
abstract: New York Liberty beats Connecticut Sun, 75-54, in WNBA opener for both teams.
lead_paragraph: Cappie Pondexter and the new acquisition Tina Charles helped the Liberty roll in Connecticut against the No. 1 draft pick Chiney Ogwumike in the opener for both teams.

headline.main: Pondexter and Charles Lead Liberty Over Sun
